CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 24, 2010

[Cite as 03/24/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-1075.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2009-2362. State ex rel. Griffin v. Stewart.

In Mandamus. On answer of respondent. On S.CtPrac.R. 10.5 determination, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
